## Completeness Checklist

- [ ] Assumption ID assigned and unique within the register
- [ ] Type correctly selected from allowed values
- [ ] Description is specific and falsifiable
- [ ] Origin phase recorded
- [ ] Validation deadline set and realistic
- [ ] Evidence availability documented
- [ ] Impact if invalid described with sufficient detail
- [ ] Linked risks identified or explicitly noted as none
- [ ] Status reflects current validation state
- [ ] Owner has acknowledged responsibility for validation
